data.description: This delightful home offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality, making it an ideal haven for you and your loved ones. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a nice piece of land and a welcoming entrance. Stepping through the front door, you'll find yourself in a spacious living room adorned with warm tones and natural light streaming through the windows. The kitchen has appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry. The home boasts three generously sized bedrooms, the master bedroom, complete with an ensuite bathroom, provides a private oasis where you can unwind after a long day.
